:192048) should be topped up before the debuff expires, then healed back up when possible<br/><b>Players targeted by (spell:191976) should be topped up before (spell:192305)<br/><b>(spell:192305) can deal moderate party-wide damage when (npc:95833) has several stacks of (spell:192132), and may require cooldowns<br/><b>Do not stand in front of (npc:95833) when she casts (spell:192018)<br/><b>Stand in the (spell:192305), but otherwise stay spread out from the party to avoid splashing (spell:191976) and (spell:192048) damage| |TANK|<b>Use a cooldown for each (spell:192018) cast<br/><b>Move (npc:95833) back and forth between (npc:97202) and (npc:97219), to avoid her gaining too many stacks of (spell:192133) or (spell:192132)<br/><b>The knock-back from (spell:192018) can be used to quickly reposition (npc:95833)<br/><b>During (spell:192132), drag (npc:95833) into the (spell:192305)<br/><b>During (spell:192133), move back from (npc:95833) as she begins to cast (spell:192307) and dodge the light orbs| 
