ay need to use a cooldown to recover<br/><b>If the tank fails to use Active Mitigation on (spell:193668), they will require heavy single-target healing<br/><b>Move into the (spell:202711)'s protective shield when (npc:95675) casts (spell:193826)<br/><b>Do not stand in patches of (spell:193702)| |TANK|<b>Pick up the (spell:202711) at the start of the fight, and after each time (npc:95675) throws it<br/><b>Use the (spell:202711) when (npc:95675) begins to cast (spell:193826)<br/><b>Do not cast any other ability while channeling the (spell:202711), or else the shield will disappear and the party will likely wipe<br/><b>Put up Active Mitigation each time (npc:95675) begins to cast (spell:193668), to avoid gaining the (spell:193686) debuff<br/><b>Move (npc:95675) away from patches of (spell:193702)| 
