3) left behind by (spell:212030)| |TANK|<b>Move (npc:98206) away from nearby (spell:197776)s and (spell:220443) pools<br/><b>Quickly pick up the (npc:98772)s when they land<br/><b>Bank Active Mitigation for when you are tanking (npc:98772)s and (npc:98206), as the combined melee damage is very high, especially with (spell:197810)<br/><b>Dodge the (spell:197788) from flying (npc:98772)s<br/><b>When (npc:98206) casts (spell:212030), step to the side or behind him to avoid being struck| 
