ase 3, the tank will require heavy healing, especially when (npc:115730) are active<br/><b>Dispel the (spell:229083) and (spell:230002) debuffs from the tank between (spell:229159) casts| |TANK|<b>Tank (npc:114790) in the center of the encounter space<br/><b>Interrupt (spell:229083)<br/><b>Use cooldowns if you reach 3+ stacks of the (spell:229083) DoT or if you are targeted by (spell:229159)<br/><b>Move out of the path of (spell:229151) and incoming (spell:229161) orbs<br/><b>During Phases 1 and 2, avoid standing in the (spell:229287) impact zones<br/><b>Take the (spell:229610) to the Legion Command Ship on each phase transition<br/><b>At the start of Phase 2, assess the direction of (npc:114790)'s (spell:229151) casts and step onto the sides of the ship if necessary to avoid them<br/><b>Try to be the first player to reach (npc:114790) in Phase 2<br/><b>At the start of Phase 3, drag the 6 (npc:115730) to the boss<br/><b>Pick up the two new (npc:115730) that spawn shortly after arriving and again every 25 seconds| 
