hen the (npc:102271)s spawn to keep the party alive while players kill (npc:102271)s<br/><b>If possible, dispel (spell:202300) from players who drop low in health<br/><b>When targeted by (spell:202341), adjust your positioning so no other players will be struck by it| |TANK|<b>Use Active Mitigation or a defensive cooldown for each (spell:202217)<br/><b>Damage-reduction cooldowns are more powerful than reactive healing cooldowns since (spell:202217) reduces your healing taken| 
