s 1 to cast (spell:202805) on them<br/><b>Only bite the tank if absolutely necessary to avoid (spell:202804)<br/><b>Try to deal damage as often as possible so the (spell:202779) buff is useful<br/><b>Move away from (spell:203364) pools near you<br/><b>As more players become Vampyr, the party will take less damage, but keep an eye on tank healing| |TANK|<b>Move (npc:102614) away from the (spell:203364) pools that form beneath her feet<br/><b>If any players are affected by (spell:202804), use cooldowns to survive their damage, and assist in interrupting or crowd-controlling the hostile players| 
