overed second level of the dungeon to avoid the (spell:201960)<br/><b>Use personal damage-reduction CDs as the (spell:201960) is about to land, to mitigate the burst damage<br/><b>Break out any allies who have become (spell:202037) by attacking the Ice Block they are encased in| |HEAL|<b>Tank damage will be heavy during (spell:201379), and may require focused healing or your single-target CDs<br/><b>Do not dispel the (spell:201379) debuff from the tank until (npc:101951) has stopped channeling (spell:201379)<br/><b>Stay away from (npc:101951)'s tail to avoid (spell:201354) knockbacks<br/><b>Move out of (spell:201672) impact areas<br/><b>When (npc:101951) flies up into the air, run onto the (spell:201957)-covered second level of the dungeon to avoid the (spell:201960)<br/><b>Party healing will be needed after each (spell:201960); use throughput CDs here| |TANK|<b>Use a CD for each (spell:201379)<br/><b>Tank with your back to a wall to avoid the knockback from (spell:201355)<br/><b>When (npc:101951) flies up into the air, run onto the (spell:201957)-covered second level of the dungeon to avoid the (spell:201960)| 
